title: What should we buy next?
body:
The most recently concluded snapshot has told us that the community is keen on purchasing an ape from the BAYC collection. We will be holding a vote that includes the original cats from all our previous snapshots, and also adding BAYC as an option.

The options are:
1. Cool Cats
2. Moon Cats
3. Cup Cats
4. Gutter Cats
5. Mutant Cats
6. BAYC ape

We understand that the community is feeling some apprehension from the Opensea fiasco. Rest assured, we are trying to resolve this matter. 

Nevertheless, the show must go on. Vote for your preferred option and we will proceed with that choice.
